latest done task:
Phase 3a is in the bag. Moving to Phase 3b — the class detail page.
Quick recap of what 3b adds, so you know what to expect when it's working:

Header shows name / section / semester clearly, with a copy button next to the invite code (no more raw text)
Below the header: a small panel showing invite code status (active/expired/disabled) with Reset and Disable/Enable buttons
Tabs change from Stream / Modules / People / Grades → Stream / Modules / Activities / Students / Grades
The Students tab (formerly People) now shows pending join requests at the top with Approve/Reject buttons, then the enrolled roster, with a Remove button per student
"Activities" is just a stub for now — that's a future session

